---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Emmanuel Gutiérrez Pizarro - Data, AI & territorial intelligence">

  <!-- ========== ENGLISH ========== -->
  <div class="lang-en">
    <div class="container">
      <section class="hero">
        <div>
          <h1>Emmanuel Gutiérrez Pizarro</h1>
          <p class="hero-tagline">Director, JP Asesores &amp; Researcher, ADC &middot; Building partnerships in data, AI and territorial intelligence</p>
          <p class="hero-desc">
            Consultant in innovation, data science and territorial intelligence. For 13+ years I have
            turned evidence into decisions with social organizations, communities and institutions across
            Costa Rica and Central America. My focus now: systems thinking and complex systems,
            applied AI for social and collective good, data sovereignty, and capacity building.
            I'd love to talk about data science applied to territories and the problems of the future.
          </p>
          <div class="hero-btns">
            <a href="/contacto" class="btn btn-primary">Get in touch</a>
            <a href="/files/emmanuel-gutierrez-profile-en.pdf" class="btn btn-outline" target="_blank">Download profile</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="avatar">
          <img src="/img/profile.jpg" alt="Emmanuel Gutiérrez Pizarro" />
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class="stats-bar">
        <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">13+</div><div class="stat-label">Years of experience</div></div>
        <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">60+</div><div class="stat-label">Organizations served</div></div>
        <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">95.1%</div><div class="stat-label">Nosara Census coverage</div></div>
        <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">$55M+</div><div class="stat-label">Fiscal gap quantified</div></div>
      </div>

      <section class="areas">
        <p class="section-tag">Currently</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">What I'm building now</h2>
        <div class="pub-section" style="margin-top: 1rem;">
          <div class="pub-item"><div class="pub-meta"><h3>Operating Systems for Territorial Intelligence <span class="pub-badge">In progress</span></h3><div class="pub-source">Framework - Census + Fiscal Balance + Mapa de Voces de Nosara</div></div></div>
          <div class="pub-item"><div class="pub-meta"><h3>History of Nosara <span class="pub-badge">In progress</span></h3><div class="pub-source">Editorial project - Archival research + oral history of founding families</div></div></div>
          <div class="pub-item"><div class="pub-meta"><h3>Sustainable and Regenerative Development for Nosara <span class="pub-badge">In progress</span></h3><div class="pub-source">Applied research - Territorial reordering models grounded in the data</div></div></div>
          <div class="pub-item"><div class="pub-meta"><h3>Territorial Fiscal Balance - methodology replication <span class="pub-badge">In progress</span></h3><div class="pub-source">Open methodology - Transferable to other districts and municipalities</div></div></div>
          <div class="pub-item"><div class="pub-meta"><h3>Digital Twins, Heat Maps and Policy for the Future <span class="pub-badge">In progress</span></h3><div class="pub-source">R&amp;D - Real-time territorial twins + interactive policy simulation</div></div></div>
          <div class="pub-item"><div class="pub-meta"><h3>Agentic, Internet-AI Native Institutions <span class="pub-badge">In progress</span></h3><div class="pub-source">Applied research - Governance for the era of agentic AI and an internet-native public</div></div></div>
          <div class="pub-item"><div class="pub-meta"><h3>Predictive models for territorial decisions <span class="pub-badge">In progress</span></h3><div class="pub-source">Methodology - Auditable models with a 6-check protocol, simple-to-complex catalog</div></div></div>
          <div class="pub-item"><div class="pub-meta"><h3>Governance models, cycle-breaking, resilience and community-institutional restoration <span class="pub-badge">In progress</span></h3><div class="pub-source">Applied research - Three-function framework (Architect, Oracle, Cycle-breaker)</div></div></div>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-top: 1.25rem;"><a href="/publicaciones" class="btn btn-outline">See full details in Publications</a></div>
      </section>

      <section class="areas">
        <p class="section-tag">Focus</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">What I work on</h2>
        <div class="areas-grid">
          <div class="area-card">
            <div class="area-icon fiscal"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="1 6 1 22 8 18 16 22 23 18 23 2 16 6 8 2 1 6"/><line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="18"/><line x1="16" y1="6" x2="16" y2="22"/></svg></div>
            <h3>Territorial intelligence</h3>
            <p>Subnational fiscal and territorial balances, data systems and evidence for decisions at the district and municipal level.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="area-card">
            <div class="area-icon finance"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="18" y1="20" x2="18" y2="10"/><line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="4"/><line x1="6" y1="20" x2="6" y2="14"/></svg></div>
            <h3>Data science</h3>
            <p>Analysis, indicators and data systems that turn raw information into usable evidence for action.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="area-card">
            <div class="area-icon data"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="4" r="2"/><circle cx="4" cy="18" r="2"/><circle cx="20" cy="18" r="2"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2"/><line x1="12" y1="6" x2="12" y2="10"/><line x1="10.5" y1="13.5" x2="5.5" y2="16.5"/><line x1="13.5" y1="13.5" x2="18.5" y2="16.5"/><line x1="6" y1="18" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg></div>
            <h3>Systems thinking and complex systems</h3>
            <p>Reading territories as complex adaptive systems: feedback loops, leverage points and emergent dynamics. The next chapter of how I work.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="area-card">
            <div class="area-icon fiscal"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><ellipse cx="12" cy="5" rx="9" ry="3"/><path d="M3 5v6c0 1.66 4 3 9 3s9-1.34 9-3V5"/><path d="M3 11v6c0 1.66 4 3 9 3s9-1.34 9-3v-6"/></svg></div>
            <h3>Knowledge engineering for AI</h3>
            <p>Curated knowledge graphs, ontologies and auditable data systems — the foundation that makes RAG and agentic AI actually work. Domain-specific, evidence-graded, replicable.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="area-card">
            <div class="area-icon funds"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="4" y="4" width="16" height="16" rx="2"/><rect x="9" y="9" width="6" height="6"/><line x1="9" y1="1" x2="9" y2="4"/><line x1="15" y1="1" x2="15" y2="4"/><line x1="9" y1="20" x2="9" y2="23"/><line x1="15" y1="20" x2="15" y2="23"/><line x1="20" y1="9" x2="23" y2="9"/><line x1="20" y1="14" x2="23" y2="14"/><line x1="1" y1="9" x2="4" y2="9"/><line x1="1" y1="14" x2="4" y2="14"/></svg></div>
            <h3>Applied AI for social good</h3>
            <p>Artificial intelligence applied to social and collective challenges, from automation to territorial analysis.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="area-card">
            <div class="area-icon fiscal"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg></div>
            <h3>Data sovereignty</h3>
            <p>Community and territorial control over data: who collects it, who owns it, who decides with it.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="area-card">
            <div class="area-icon finance"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 10L12 5 2 10l10 5 10-5z"/><path d="M6 12v5c0 1 2 3 6 3s6-2 6-3v-5"/></svg></div>
            <h3>Training and education</h3>
            <p>Capacity building and education so that tools, methods and data literacy stay in the territory.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="area-card">
            <div class="area-icon data"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="6"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2"/></svg></div>
            <h3>Impact evaluation</h3>
            <p>Measurement of outcomes and impact for programs, projects and public interventions.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="projects">
        <p class="section-tag">Selected work</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Work with impact</h2>
        <div class="project-list">
          <div class="project-item"><div class="project-year">2024</div><div class="project-info"><h3>Nosara Community Census</h3><p>First district-level census in Costa Rica, with 95.1% household coverage and technical advisory from INEC. Foundation of the Operating Systems for Territorial Intelligence framework.</p><div class="project-tags"><span class="tag tag-data">Data</span><span class="tag tag-fiscal">Territorial</span></div></div></div>
          <div class="project-item"><div class="project-year">2026</div><div class="project-info"><h3>Nosara Territorial Fiscal Balance</h3><p>First district-level fiscal study in the country. Quantified gap above USD 55M per year. Cadastral gap factor of 12.1x.</p><div class="project-tags"><span class="tag tag-fiscal">Territorial</span></div></div></div>
          <div class="project-item"><div class="project-year">2026</div><div class="project-info"><h3>Operating Systems for Territorial Intelligence</h3><p>Framework integrating fiscal analysis, census data and participatory governance (Mapa de Voces de Nosara) + SIG cartography + 30 locality reports. First field deployment: the district of Nosara.</p><div class="project-tags"><span class="tag tag-data">Data</span><span class="tag tag-fiscal">Territorial</span></div></div></div>
          <div class="project-item"><div class="project-year">2024 - now</div><div class="project-info"><h3>Territorial Knowledge Graph</h3><p>Operational knowledge graph with 390+ typed nodes, 790+ semantic edges and a graduated-truth protocol. Built as the foundation for RAG and agentic workflows in territorial analysis. Live deployment.</p><div class="project-tags"><span class="tag tag-data">Data</span><span class="tag tag-model">AI</span></div></div></div>
          <div class="project-item"><div class="project-year">2013 - 2020</div><div class="project-info"><h3>Entrepreneurship, innovation and early-stage support</h3><p>13 years of experience in entrepreneurship, innovation and early-stage venture support. Program Coordinator at Yo Emprendedor 2013-2020.</p><div class="project-tags"><span class="tag tag-model">Model</span></div></div></div>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-top: 1.5rem;"><a href="/proyectos" class="btn btn-outline">See all work</a></div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ========== ESPANOL ========== -->
  <div class="lang-es">
    <div class="container">
      <section class="hero">
        <div>
          <h1>Emmanuel Gutiérrez Pizarro</h1>
          <p class="hero-tagline">Director, JP Asesores e Investigador, ADC &middot; Construyendo alianzas en datos, IA e inteligencia territorial</p>
          <p class="hero-desc">
            Consultor en innovación, ciencia de datos e inteligencia territorial. Desde hace más de 13 años
            convierto evidencia en decisiones junto a organizaciones sociales, comunidades e instituciones en
            Costa Rica y Centroamérica. Mi foco hoy: pensamiento sistémico y sistemas complejos,
            inteligencia artificial aplicada a lo social y colectivo, soberanía de datos, y capacitación.
            Me encantaría conversar sobre ciencia de datos aplicada a los territorios y los problemas del futuro.
          </p>
          <div class="hero-btns">
            <a href="/contacto" class="btn btn-primary">Contacto</a>
            <a href="/files/emmanuel-gutierrez-perfil-es.pdf" class="btn btn-outline" target="_blank">Descargar perfil</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="avatar">
          <img src="/img/profile.jpg" alt="Emmanuel Gutiérrez Pizarro" />
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class="stats-bar">
        <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">13+</div><div class="stat-label">Años de experiencia</div></div>
        <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">60+</div><div class="stat-label">Organizaciones atendidas</div></div>
        <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">95.1%</div><div class="stat-label">Cobertura Censo Nosara</div></div>
        <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">$55M+</div><div class="stat-label">Brecha fiscal cuantificada</div></div>
      </div>

      <section class="areas">
        <p class="section-tag">Ahora</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">En lo que estoy trabajando</h2>
        <div class="pub-section" style="margin-top: 1rem;">
          <div class="pub-item"><div class="pub-meta"><h3>Sistemas Operativos para Inteligencia Territorial <span class="pub-badge">En curso</span></h3><div class="pub-source">Framework - Censo + Balance Fiscal + Mapa de Voces de Nosara</div></div></div>
          <div class="pub-item"><div class="pub-meta"><h3>Historia de Nosara <span class="pub-badge">En curso</span></h3><div class="pub-source">Proyecto editorial - Investigación de archivo + historia oral de las familias fundadoras</div></div></div>
          <div class="pub-item"><div class="pub-meta"><h3>Desarrollo sostenible y regenerativo para Nosara <span class="pub-badge">En curso</span></h3><div class="pub-source">Investigación aplicada - Modelos de reordenamiento territorial basados en datos</div></div></div>
          <div class="pub-item"><div class="pub-meta"><h3>Balance Fiscal Territorial - replicación metodológica <span class="pub-badge">En curso</span></h3><div class="pub-source">Metodología abierta - Transferible a otros distritos y municipalidades</div></div></div>
          <div class="pub-item"><div class="pub-meta"><h3>Gemelos digitales, mapas de calor y política pública para el futuro <span class="pub-badge">En curso</span></h3><div class="pub-source">I+D - Gemelos territoriales en tiempo real + simulación interactiva de política</div></div></div>
          <div class="pub-item"><div class="pub-meta"><h3>Instituciones nativas de Agentic e Internet-AI <span class="pub-badge">En curso</span></h3><div class="pub-source">Investigación aplicada - Gobernanza para la era de IA agéntica y un público nativo de internet</div></div></div>
          <div class="pub-item"><div class="pub-meta"><h3>Modelos predictivos para decisiones territoriales <span class="pub-badge">En curso</span></h3><div class="pub-source">Metodología - Modelos auditables con protocolo de 6 chequeos, catálogo simple→complejo</div></div></div>
          <div class="pub-item"><div class="pub-meta"><h3>Modelos de gobernanza, ruptura de ciclos, resiliencia y restauración comunitaria-institucional <span class="pub-badge">En curso</span></h3><div class="pub-source">Investigación aplicada - Marco de tres funciones (Arquitecto, Oráculo, Ruptura de Ciclo)</div></div></div>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-top: 1.25rem;"><a href="/publicaciones" class="btn btn-outline">Ver detalle en Publicaciones</a></div>
      </section>

      <section class="areas">
        <p class="section-tag">Foco</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">En qué trabajo</h2>
        <div class="areas-grid">
          <div class="area-card">
            <div class="area-icon fiscal"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="1 6 1 22 8 18 16 22 23 18 23 2 16 6 8 2 1 6"/><line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="18"/><line x1="16" y1="6" x2="16" y2="22"/></svg></div>
            <h3>Inteligencia territorial</h3>
            <p>Balances fiscales y territoriales subnacionales, sistemas de datos y evidencia para decisiones a nivel distrital y municipal.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="area-card">
            <div class="area-icon finance"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="18" y1="20" x2="18" y2="10"/><line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="4"/><line x1="6" y1="20" x2="6" y2="14"/></svg></div>
            <h3>Ciencia de datos</h3>
            <p>Análisis, indicadores y sistemas de datos que convierten información en evidencia útil para la acción.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="area-card">
            <div class="area-icon data"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="4" r="2"/><circle cx="4" cy="18" r="2"/><circle cx="20" cy="18" r="2"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2"/><line x1="12" y1="6" x2="12" y2="10"/><line x1="10.5" y1="13.5" x2="5.5" y2="16.5"/><line x1="13.5" y1="13.5" x2="18.5" y2="16.5"/><line x1="6" y1="18" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg></div>
            <h3>Pensamiento sistémico y sistemas complejos</h3>
            <p>Leer los territorios como sistemas adaptativos complejos: bucles de retroalimentación, puntos de palanca y dinámicas emergentes. El siguiente capítulo de cómo trabajo.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="area-card">
            <div class="area-icon fiscal"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><ellipse cx="12" cy="5" rx="9" ry="3"/><path d="M3 5v6c0 1.66 4 3 9 3s9-1.34 9-3V5"/><path d="M3 11v6c0 1.66 4 3 9 3s9-1.34 9-3v-6"/></svg></div>
            <h3>Ingeniería del conocimiento para IA</h3>
            <p>Grafos de conocimiento curados, ontologías y sistemas de datos auditables — la base que hace que RAG e IA agéntica realmente funcionen. Específicos por dominio, con verdad graduada, replicables.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="area-card">
            <div class="area-icon funds"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="4" y="4" width="16" height="16" rx="2"/><rect x="9" y="9" width="6" height="6"/><line x1="9" y1="1" x2="9" y2="4"/><line x1="15" y1="1" x2="15" y2="4"/><line x1="9" y1="20" x2="9" y2="23"/><line x1="15" y1="20" x2="15" y2="23"/><line x1="20" y1="9" x2="23" y2="9"/><line x1="20" y1="14" x2="23" y2="14"/><line x1="1" y1="9" x2="4" y2="9"/><line x1="1" y1="14" x2="4" y2="14"/></svg></div>
            <h3>IA aplicada a lo social</h3>
            <p>Inteligencia artificial aplicada a desafíos sociales y colectivos, de la automatización al análisis territorial.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="area-card">
            <div class="area-icon fiscal"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg></div>
            <h3>Soberanía de datos</h3>
            <p>Control comunitario y territorial sobre los datos: quién los recoge, quién los posee, quién decide con ellos.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="area-card">
            <div class="area-icon finance"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 10L12 5 2 10l10 5 10-5z"/><path d="M6 12v5c0 1 2 3 6 3s6-2 6-3v-5"/></svg></div>
            <h3>Capacitación y educación</h3>
            <p>Formación y educación para que las herramientas, los métodos y la alfabetización de datos se queden en el territorio.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="area-card">
            <div class="area-icon data"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="6"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2"/></svg></div>
            <h3>Evaluación de impacto</h3>
            <p>Medición de resultados e impacto para programas, proyectos e intervenciones públicas.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="projects">
        <p class="section-tag">Proyectos destacados</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Trabajo con impacto</h2>
        <div class="project-list">
          <div class="project-item"><div class="project-year">2024</div><div class="project-info"><h3>Censo Comunitario de Nosara</h3><p>Primer censo a nivel de distrito en Costa Rica. Cobertura del 95.1% de hogares, con asesoría técnica del INEC. Base del framework Sistemas Operativos para Inteligencia Territorial.</p><div class="project-tags"><span class="tag tag-data">Datos</span><span class="tag tag-fiscal">Territorial</span></div></div></div>
          <div class="project-item"><div class="project-year">2026</div><div class="project-info"><h3>Balance Fiscal Territorial de Nosara</h3><p>Primer estudio fiscal a nivel de distrito en el país. Brecha cuantificada superior a USD 55 millones anuales. Factor de brecha catastral de 12.1x.</p><div class="project-tags"><span class="tag tag-fiscal">Territorial</span></div></div></div>
          <div class="project-item"><div class="project-year">2026</div><div class="project-info"><h3>Sistemas Operativos para Inteligencia Territorial</h3><p>Framework que integra análisis fiscal, datos censales y gobernanza participativa (Mapa de Voces de Nosara) + cartografía SIG + 30 reportes a nivel de localidad. Primer despliegue en campo: el distrito de Nosara.</p><div class="project-tags"><span class="tag tag-data">Datos</span><span class="tag tag-fiscal">Territorial</span></div></div></div>
          <div class="project-item"><div class="project-year">2024 - hoy</div><div class="project-info"><h3>Grafo de Conocimiento Territorial</h3><p>Grafo de conocimiento operacional con 390+ nodos tipados, 790+ aristas semánticas y un protocolo de verdad graduada. Construido como base para flujos RAG y agénticos en análisis territorial. Despliegue activo.</p><div class="project-tags"><span class="tag tag-data">Datos</span><span class="tag tag-model">IA</span></div></div></div>
          <div class="project-item"><div class="project-year">2013 - 2020</div><div class="project-info"><h3>Emprendimiento, innovación y apoyo a proyectos en fase temprana</h3><p>13 años de experiencia en emprendimiento, innovación y apoyo a proyectos en fase temprana. Coordinador de Programas en Yo Emprendedor 2013-2020.</p><div class="project-tags"><span class="tag tag-model">Modelo</span></div></div></div>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-top: 1.5rem;"><a href="/proyectos" class="btn btn-outline">Ver todos los proyectos</a></div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>

</Layout>
